- Enables: "Assertion X used exact factual state Y at generation N"

**Operations**
- Explicit reload (`cmdb_reload()`)
- Thread-safe (RLock only during reload)
- Atomic swap (no partial state exposed)
- Zero dataset mutations from the engine

