| `cmdb/` | Core API | All Python code, models, rules, validation |
| `tests/` | Testing | Single test suite (no redundancy) |
| `docs/` | Documentation | All `.md` files (architecture, philosophy, patterns, error logs) |
| `examples/` | Examples | 5 canonical YAML files (asset, software, endpoint, automation, agent) |
| `integrations/` | Integrations | Wrappers for specific platforms (Hermes today, others tomorrow) |
| `scripts/` | Tooling | General-purpose CLI wrappers (e.g., `cmdb`, `update-github-meta.sh`, `run_pilot.py`, `grounding_pilot.py`) |
| `data/` | Dataset | **Empty in repo** — production data lives in `~/knowledge/knowledge-kernel/` |

