### Code ≠ Data (Explicit Separation)

The `data/` directory is **intentionally empty** in version control. Production datasets:
- Live externally (`~/knowledge/knowledge-kernel/`)
- Are excluded via `.gitignore`
- Change frequently (daily discoveries, updates)
- Are environment-specific (your infra ≠ mine)
- May contain sensitive details (hostnames, IPs, configurations)

